# - Relative time expressions: "in 2 minutes", "in 1 hour", "in 3 days", "in 1 week"
# - Natural language scheduling with Google Gemini AI
# - JWT authentication with 7-day token expiry
# - Rate limiting: 100 requests per 15 minutes
